+ kigarashi@users.sourceforge.net
-------------------------------------------

1. What is this?
  Simple bindings for SDL API.

2. How to install
  > make -f linux32_.mk

  dig .konoha/sdl directory at your launcing directory.
if you checkout svn repository, its easy to make symlink
from your $(homedir),

  > ln -s $(svn-package-checkoutdir) ~/.konoha

3. How to Use?
  For detailed build and API reference, see the project
web site:
    
          http://konoha.sourceforge.jp/wiki

  For quickly use, check out sample files.

  > konoha sample/sample2.k

4. Bugs
  report is always welcome.

  kigarashi@users.sourceforge.jp
